  <name>Vortex</name>
  <summary>Mod manager for PC games</summary>

  <!-- TODO: Placeholder text. Adapted from README by LLM. -->
  <description>
    <p>
      Vortex is the open-source mod manager from Nexus Mods. It is designed to make modding
      your game as simple as possible for new users, while still providing enough control
      for more experienced veterans of the modding scene.
    </p>
    <p>
      Vortex takes complex tasks such as sorting your load order or managing your mod files
      and automates as much of the process as possible, with the goal of achieving a stable
      modded game with minimal effort. Spend less time modding and more time playing your games.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-game support for over 500 different games</li>
      <li>Seamless integration with Nexus Mods for easy mod discovery and installation</li>
      <li>Built-in auto-sorting system for load order management</li>
      <li>Powerful yet easy-to-use plugin management</li>
      <li>Mod profiles for independent mod configurations</li>
      <li>Modern, customizable user interface</li>
      <li>Extension framework for community plugins</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

